Package: ClaudeAgentSDK
Title: R SDK for Claude Code Agent
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Kaiping", "Yang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "1260146556@qq.com")
Description: Provides an R interface to the Claude Code CLI, spawning it as a
    subprocess and communicating via newline-delimited JSON stream protocol with
    full bidirectional control (permission requests, hooks, interrupt). Supports
    multi-turn conversations, streaming output, Shiny integration, and session
    management. Mirrors the Python claude-agent-sdk API. Unofficial community
    port, not affiliated with or endorsed by Anthropic.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Language: en-US
URL: https://kaipingyang.github.io/ClaudeAgentSDK/, https://github.com/kaipingyang/ClaudeAgentSDK
BugReports: https://github.com/kaipingyang/ClaudeAgentSDK/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    processx (>= 3.8.0),
    jsonlite,
    R6,
    later,
    coro,
    rlang (>= 1.0.0)
Suggests:
    promises,
    shiny,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
SystemRequirements: Claude Code CLI (>= 2.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
